text: <../images/tbar.gif>be suðan þam brocesXXXacera<../images/tbar.gif>eft to þam broce andlong broces<../images/tbar.gif>on.
Andlong broces to þam ealdan stræte up andlong stræte be <halh>.
<../images/tbar.gif>west on þone feld up rihte wið þrim gemærum andlong heges to <ald>.
Be fif acerum in ða lacu andlong þære lace.
Norþmestan fennes in brocces broc<../images/tbar.gif>eft in <diling>.
